cdata.name: HeavyCoin
cdata.desc: HeavyCoin is another unique crypto Currency with its Hefty1 algorithm to encourage CPU mining only. The coin is secure due to its SHA-256 Keccak-512, Blake-512 combination. The coin also has pegged difficulty retargetting and a decentralised block reward voting. Otherwise a block time of 2 mins and Kimoto Gravity well temporal retargetting.
